  "text": "Algorithm MLSM computes a meo and the associated minimal triangulation of the input graph G. It computes a mmo of G if the order on labels is total [CITATION_1] . It can be modified into Algorithms Moplex-MLSM computing a mmo of G whether the order on labels is total or not, which can be extended to Algorithms MLSM-CliqueTree and DCL-MLSM-CliqueTree computing a mmo, the associated minimal triangulation H of G, a clique tree and the minimal separators of H. Below are algorithms Moplex-MLSM and DCL-MLSM-CliqueTree.",
